source: crates/daemon/tests/cli_help.rs
expression: stdout
---
Export a thread or matching search results

Usage: mxr export [OPTIONS] [THREAD_ID]

Arguments:
  [THREAD_ID]  

Options:
      --search <SEARCH>  
      --format <FORMAT>  [default: markdown]
      --output <OUTPUT>  
  -h, --help             Print help
